This paper is primarily focused on the performance of deep neural networks, specifically sparse neural networks. The most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper discusses the training behavior of neural networks. The second likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as the paper specifically focuses on sparse neural networks. The third likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), as the paper discusses the accuracy of sparse neural networks. The fourth likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), as the paper discusses the design and performance of neural networks. The fifth likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), as the paper discusses the efficiency of training sparse neural networks.
